section CondAb

/-

# Condensed abelian groups

Condensed abelian groups form an abelian category satisfying
Grothendieck's axioms AB3, AB3*, AB4, AB4*, AB5 (and AB6, which
has not been implemented in mathlib).

-/

#check CondensedAb.{u}

